Package: americorps.gov
Title: API Client for data.americorps.gov
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained Socrata SODA API client for data.americorps.gov.
    Access AmeriCorps NCCC deployments, Segal Education Award payments,
    member exit surveys, civic engagement data, demographics, research grants,
    and more. All functions return tibbles.
